# Phase 6 Plan 06-01 Task 2 — decl_func.iron expected-scopes reference.
# Human-readable companion to the inline `// <-` / `// ^` assertions in
# decl_func.iron. Consumed by reviewers; vscode-tmgrammar-test reads the
# inline assertions in the .iron file directly.

Token         | Scope
--------------|------------------------------------------
func          | keyword.declaration.iron
main          | entity.name.function.iron
(             | punctuation.section.iron
)             | punctuation.section.iron
->            | keyword.operator.iron
int           | (unscoped — lowercase type, no uppercase heuristic)
{             | punctuation.section.iron
return        | keyword.control.iron
0             | constant.numeric.integer.iron
}             | punctuation.section.iron

Covers UI-SPEC S6 scopes:
- keyword.declaration.iron
- entity.name.function.iron
- keyword.control.iron
- constant.numeric.integer.iron
- punctuation.section.iron
